# Week 2 - Iris Flower Classification 🌸

## 📌 Description
This project focuses on classifying Iris flowers using Machine Learning.

## 🧠 What I Learned
- Training and Testing datasets
- How machine learning models learn patterns
- Model prediction
- Accuracy evaluation
- Confusion Matrix
- F1 Score

## ⚙️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Jupyter Notebook

## 📊 Dataset
Iris Dataset

## 🚀 Outcome
Built a classification model and understood the importance of evaluating models on unseen test data.
